                    <span>The Spanish Civil War has been called the most lied about event of the 20th Century. Capa's photographs are powerful, but just another addition to the long line of western artists and intellectuals who surrendered their minds and talents to the service of Stalin and the Comintern during the 1930s. It is a shame that the myth of the good "republican" cause in Spain continues to be perpetuated.</span>
                  
              
